---
// Footer component following Vercel design system
---

<footer class="bg-canvas border-t border-hairline mt-auto">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- About -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-3 text-ink">About</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-body leading-relaxed">
          A free, privacy-first background remover that runs entirely in your browser. Your images never leave your device, so there are no uploads, no accounts, and no waiting.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Features -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-3 text-ink">Features</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-body">
          <li>✓ 100% Private, On-Device Processing</li>
          <li>✓ No Sign-Up or Watermarks</li>
          <li>✓ Unlimited Full-Resolution Downloads</li>
          <li>✓ Batch Processing with ZIP Export</li>
          <li>✓ Smart AI Engine Selection</li>
          <li>✓ Works Offline After First Load</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Use Cases -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold mb-3 text-ink">Great For</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-body">
          <li>Product photos &amp; online listings</li>
          <li>Profile pictures &amp; avatars</li>
          <li>Logos, graphics &amp; design assets</li>
          <li>Transparent stickers &amp; cutouts</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-hairline flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 text-sm text-mute">
      <nav class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-x-5 gap-y-2" aria-label="Footer">
        <a href="/" class="text-mute no-underline hover:text-ink transition-colors">Home</a>
        <a href="/about" class="text-mute no-underline hover:text-ink transition-colors">About</a>
        <a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-mute no-underline hover:text-ink transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a>
        <a href="/terms" class="text-mute no-underline hover:text-ink transition-colors">Terms &amp; Conditions</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="text-mute no-underline hover:text-ink transition-colors">Contact</a>
      </nav>
      <p class="m-0 whitespace-nowrap">&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} FreeRemoveBG. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
